One Million U.K. Water Bills to Hit $813 a Year, Telegraph Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-24T02:42:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/one-million-u-k-water-bills-to-hit-813-a-year-telegraph-says.html
Water bills for more than 1 million
households in the U.K. will rise above 500 pounds ($813) a year
on average, the  Daily Telegraph  reported, without saying where
it got the information.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
